      "content": "Let's start by plotting $(0,3)$ and $(3,7)$ and connecting the points.\n\n![](https://ka-perseus-graphie.s3.amazonaws.com/2ec9d27633dc52440d8e82fcf99c314f3fad19ff.png)",
